				<text><![CDATA[13. <b>“SECURITY”</b>means the diverse security (ies) stipulated in the Loan Agreement and/or Loan Approval Letter which the Borrower is liable to create or procure and furnish in favour of the company to secure the due repayment of the Loan and payment of other month this agreement.<br>
				14. <b>DELINQUENT:</b> means situation where borrower is late or overdue on EMI as per loan schedule. It is contractual obligation to make payment against a loan on due date as per repayment schedule.<br>
15. <b>“FLOATING RATE OF INTEREST”or “FROI”</b> means the interest rated decide by Company from time to time as its Lending rate and applied with spread / margin, if any, as may be decided by Company, on the loan of the borrower pursuant to this agreement and shall be communicated to Borrower accordingly.]]></text>
